    "For specific field program vulnerability detection, such as smart contracts and shell scripts, due to their short length and low complexity, LLMs usually have a more accurate performance.",
    "Dynamic vulnerability detectionIn the field of vulnerability detection, fuzzy testing is an efficient dynamic detection technique.",
    "It explores and detects vulnerabilities in programs by continuously constructing unexpected abnormal data and providing them to the target program for execution while monitoring program execution anomalies [480].",
